Author: an-lee <an.lee.work@gmail.com>
Date:   Fri Apr 10 09:24:55 2026 +0800

    fix(agentic): install iptables and docker-compose in runner containers for AWF

    Agentic workflows using GitHub Agentic Workflows (gh-aw) failed with
    "Failed to create DOCKER-USER chain" because the runner container lacked
    iptables. The Agent Workflow Firewall (awf) needs iptables to manage the
    DOCKER-USER chain and docker-compose to start sidecar containers.

